<BaseLayout title={'About Ryan Guth, CFP® — Goldfin Group'} description={'Ryan Guth sold his own company, wrote Permission to Exit, and founded Goldfin Group to guide founder-led owners through the largest transaction of their lives.'} path={'/about'}>
<div class="pagehead">
  <div class="wrap two-col">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">About Ryan</p>
      <h1>I've sat in <em>your chair.</em></h1>
      <div class="prose" style="margin-top:26px">
        <p>I sold my own company about a decade ago. I know what it's like to build something that structures your schedule, your identity, and your family's life, and then to wonder what's on the other side of it.</p>
        <p>That experience sent me into wealth management with one focus: founder-led owners of $7 million to $70 million businesses navigating the largest transaction of their lives, with their entire financial picture on the table, not just the accounts under management. In 2024 I published <strong>Permission to Exit: Prepare to Sell Your Business Without Regret</strong>, and as a CERTIFIED FINANCIAL PLANNER™ professional I now spend my days quarterbacking exits: before, during, and after the sale.</p>
        <p>I live in Middle Tennessee with my wife and our three boys. When I'm not working or raising my family, I enjoy CrossFit, men's ministry, and anything that comes with community built-in. The deeper mission behind Goldfin is simple: helping owners orient what they've built toward meaningful impact, so the wealth becomes a tool instead of a scoreboard.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="cta-row"><a class="btn btn-line" href="/book">Read Permission to Exit</a></div>
    </div>
    <div><div class="photo" style="aspect-ratio:4/5"><img src="/assets/ryan-about.jpg" alt="Ryan Guth portrait"></div></div>
  </div>
</div>
</BaseLayout>
